# Agent Redesign: From Linear DAG to Tool-Using ReAct Agent

## What Exists Today

### Current Architecture (Linear DAG)

```mermaid
flowchart TD
    Start --> safety["check_safety"]
    safety -->|safe| relevancy["check_relevancy"]
    safety -->|unsafe| reject["unsafe_rejector → END"]
    relevancy -->|relevant| require["require_code"]
    relevancy -->|irrelevant| general["general_purpose → END"]
    require -->|yes| plan["create_plan"]
    require -->|no| noncode["noncode_generator → END"]
    plan --> codegen["code_generator"]
    codegen --> guard["code_guard"]
    guard -->|ok| explain["explain_code → END"]
    guard -->|retry| retry["retry_code_generator → code_guard"]
    guard -->|failed| END
```

