## Frontend UX

### New SSE Events

| Event | Payload | Purpose |
|-------|---------|---------|
| `tool_call` | `{tool, args, call_id}` | Agent calling a tool |
| `tool_result` | `{call_id, output, status, duration_ms}` | Tool result |
| `tool_progress` | `{call_id, line}` | Live stdout (bash/pip) |
| `intervention_request` | `{id, prompt, options, multi_select, timeout_sec}` | Agent asks user |

### `ToolActivityCard.vue`

Inline cards in chat showing tool calls. `bash` and `pip_install` get terminal rendering:

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────┐
│ 🖥️ bash                        1.2s │
│ ┌────────────────────────────────┐   │
│ │ $ rg "revenue" --count         │   │
│ │ sales_data.csv:47              │   │
│ └────────────────────────────────┘   │
└──────────────────────────────────────┘
```

### `AgentIntervention.vue`

Rendered inline when `intervention_request` arrives. Shows prompt, options (checkboxes/radio), approve/deny. Sends `POST /chat/intervention/{id}/respond`.

### `TerminalRenderer.vue`

Dark monospace output viewer. Streams lines via `tool_progress`. Auto-scrolls. Used inside `ToolActivityCard` for `bash` and `pip_install`.

